---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

const phone = "06.51.15.57.58";
---

<MainLayout
  bannerHeight="24svh"
  seoTitle="Tarifs – Dépannage informatique à Vesoul / Pusey"
  seoDescription="Tarifs indicatifs (lancement) pour dépannage PC, Wi-Fi, imprimante, smartphones, coaching numérique autour de Vesoul / Pusey."
>
  <div class="article-wrapper">
    <div class="article" style="margin:auto;">

      <h1 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl">
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r to-lime-600 from-blue-400">
          Tarifs
        </span>
        
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg font-normal text-gray-700 lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">
        Certains tarifs sont donnés à <strong>titre indicatif</strong> (pour vous donner un ordre d'idée).
        <br>Je valide le tarif avec vous avant toute intervention.
        Pour tout renseignement, n’hésitez pas à me contacter.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-normal text-gray-700 lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">
        <span class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-blue-50 px-2 py-1 font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:bg-blue-950 dark:text-blue-300">
          Contact :
        </span>
        {" "}
        par téléphone au <span class="font-semibold">{phone}</span> ou via le{" "}
        <a
          href="/contact/"
          title="Contact / devis"
          class="font-semibold text-blue-600 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-blue-300 hover:text-blue-700 hover:decoration-blue-500
                 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-blue-400 focus-visible:ring-offset-2
                 dark:text-blue-400 dark:decoration-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-300 dark:hover:decoration-blue-400 dark:focus-visible:ring-blue-500"
        >
          formulaire de contact
        </a>.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-normal text-gray-700 lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">
        <span class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-blue-50 px-2 py-1 font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:bg-blue-950 dark:text-blue-300">
          Déplacement :
        </span>
        {" "}
        au-delà de 10 km depuis mon domicile : <span class="font-semibold">forfait déplacement 10 €</span>.  
        Je me déplace dans un rayon de <span class="font-semibold">30 km maximum</span> autour de Vesoul.
        <br>
         je propose un tarif volontairement bas
      </p>


      {/* ===================== Dépannage PC ===================== */}
      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-blue-400 dark:text-gray-300 md:text-3xl">
        Dépannage PC & optimisation
      </h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-black/5 dark:ring-white/10">
        <table class="w-full text-sm lg:text-base">
          <thead class="bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5">
            <tr>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Prestation</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap">Tarif lancement</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="align-top">
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Diagnostic / analyse</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">15 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Nettoyage logiciel + optimisation (PC lent, démarrage, MAJ…)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">35–49 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Mot de passe oublié (si réinitialisation possible)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">25–39 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Sauvegarde simple (disque externe et/ou cloud) + explications</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">29–49 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Transfert vers un nouveau PC (docs, photos, favoris…)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">49–79 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Installation / réinstallation Windows (propre + réglages de base)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">69–99 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Installation / dual-boot Linux + prise en main</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">79–109 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"><strong>Récupération de données</strong> (selon état du disque)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"><strong>à partir de 49 €</strong></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-normal text-gray-700 lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">
        La récupération de données varie beaucoup (disque fatigué, secteurs HS, chiffrement…) : je fais un devis après diagnostic.
      </p>

      {/* ===================== Wi-Fi / Imprimante ===================== */}
      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-blue-400 dark:text-gray-300 md:text-3xl">
        Wi-Fi, box internet, imprimante
      </h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-black/5 dark:ring-white/10">
        <table class="w-full text-sm lg:text-base">
          <thead class="bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5">
            <tr>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Prestation</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap">Tarif lancement</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="align-top">
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Diagnostic / optimisation Wi-Fi (box, stabilité, couverture)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">29–59 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Installation / configuration imprimante & scanner (USB ou Wi-Fi)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">25–45 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Partage imprimante / fichiers (plusieurs appareils)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">29–49 €</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      {/* ===================== Téléphone / Tablette ===================== */}
      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-blue-400 dark:text-gray-300 md:text-3xl">
        Téléphones & tablettes
      </h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-black/5 dark:ring-white/10">
        <table class="w-full text-sm lg:text-base">
          <thead class="bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5">
            <tr>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Prestation</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap">Tarif lancement</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="align-top">
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Prise en main Android (réglages, stockage, applis utiles)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">25 € / h</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Sauvegarde / transfert vers nouveau téléphone (WhatsApp, photos, contacts…)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">35–59 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Nettoyage + remise à zéro (sauvegarde puis réinitialisation propre)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">29–49 €</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      {/* ===================== Cours / Coaching ===================== */}
      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-blue-400 dark:text-gray-300 md:text-3xl">
        Cours informatique & coaching
      </h2>

      <p class="text-lg font-normal text-gray-700 lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">
        Le but : vous rendre autonome, à votre rythme, sans stress, sans jargon.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-black/5 dark:ring-white/10">
        <table class="w-full text-sm lg:text-base">
          <thead class="bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5">
            <tr>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Prestation</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap">Tarif lancement</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="align-top">
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Cours / assistance (Windows, fichiers, Internet, emails…)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">25 € / h</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Organisation photos & documents (classement, doublons, sauvegarde)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">35–59 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Gestionnaire de mots de passe (Bitwarden…) + mini-cours</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">29–49 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Sécurité de base (arnaques, phishing, bonnes habitudes)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">25–45 €</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      {/* ===================== Web / Outils ===================== */}
      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-blue-400 dark:text-gray-300 md:text-3xl">
        Développement web & outils sur mesure
      </h2>

      <p class="text-lg font-normal text-gray-700 lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">
        C’est variable : je travaille au <strong>devis</strong>. Pour donner un ordre d’idée :
      </p>

      <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-black/5 dark:ring-white/10">
        <table class="w-full text-sm lg:text-base">
          <thead class="bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5">
            <tr>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Prestation</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap">Tarif indicatif</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="align-top">
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Petits correctifs / maintenance légère</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">35–50 € / h</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Site vitrine simple (quelques pages)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">à partir de 450 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Blog / site plus complet</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">à partir de 750 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Automatisation (scripts, petits outils)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">sur devis</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">WebGL / 3D (démo, animation, présentation produit)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">sur devis</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      {/* ===================== Divers ===================== */}
      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-blue-400 dark:text-gray-300 md:text-3xl">
        Divers / coup de main numérique
      </h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-black/5 dark:ring-white/10">
        <table class="w-full text-sm lg:text-base">
          <thead class="bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5">
            <tr>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Prestation</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap">Tarif lancement</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="align-top">
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Conseils avant achat (PC, imprimante, routeur…)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">15–29 €</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Coup de main (comprendre + faire ensemble)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">25 € / h</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      {/* ===================== CTA ===================== */}
      <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl bg-blue-50 px-5 py-5 dark:bg-blue-950/40">
        <p class="text-lg font-normal text-gray-800 lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-200">
          Décrivez votre souci en 2 lignes, et je vous réponds avec une estimation rapide.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-normal text-gray-700 lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            title="Demander un devis"
            class="font-semibold text-blue-600 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-blue-300 hover:text-blue-700 hover:decoration-blue-500
                   focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-blue-400 focus-visible:ring-offset-2
                   dark:text-blue-400 dark:decoration-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-300 dark:hover:decoration-blue-400 dark:focus-visible:ring-blue-500"
          >
            Demander un devis / poser une question
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style is:global>
  /* Même “largeur / padding” que ta home */
  .main-container {
    max-width: 100% !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
    padding-left: 0 !important;
    padding-right: 0 !important;
  }
  .main-container > .flex.flex-row.items-start > .space-y-8 {
    flex: 1 1 auto;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .article-wrapper {
    @apply mx-3 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--card-color)] px-5 py-6 lg:mx-0 lg:px-10 lg:py-9;
  }
  .article {
    @apply flex flex-col;
    font-size: var(--primary-font);
  }
</style>
